Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久 就要到殖民卫星法丁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 资料有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殖民卫星 法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史悠久 规模最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商业农业样样繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特也没精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…最近累坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手又痒痒了 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗这东西会上瘾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦体验过那种兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平的日常生活就会变得索然无味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…只是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 不想去和平的托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想继续战斗的男人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但UE如果不停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能不打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也在对我说要我用高达保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说你不想去托尔迪亚没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 和我无关就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我关心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了 只有那台白色机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果去托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西自然归我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受和平去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达绝不会让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后咱们大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 菲利特是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须想办法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被监察局专门传唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道为什么吧 古鲁迪克中校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不明白你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少给我装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有司令部的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就私自担任歌姬号舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自命令舰船出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明显违反军纪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达法丁后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会第一时间拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军事法庭伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么优秀的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有选择手段的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天体仪发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主、副、后备网络 均无法连接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然无法连接天体仪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法与外界取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能逃离诺拉前系统就有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有多久抵达法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用近距离可视光线通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与法丁取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给出宇宙港的图像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是殖民卫星法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到信号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许贵舰入港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请遵从指示 采取入港航行状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是歌姬号 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按指示航道入港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 不能只顾着高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快整理行李
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是法丁吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 太棒了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空港就这么豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克 别那么兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天不想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 真不给面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 今天就我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事 想一个人呆会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩算什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克·艾诺亚中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军监察局已经下令拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰歌姬号 根据当地标准时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在殖民卫星法丁滞留六天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经被下令拘留了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查了你在法丁银行的秘密账户
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受违法收入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许没有入港许可的船只通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果被拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些也会在军事法庭上公之于众
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好在 最起码现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事 只有你知我知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长…长官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克中校的拘捕任务…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的嫌疑已经洗清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 古鲁迪克中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都获得在法丁的滞留许可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说结束就结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许再追究这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是古鲁迪克舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道你会来 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想问您！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迄今为止 只是想着击败UE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须真正意义上变强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则没法拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 怎么才能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 是我东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里别动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话来我们船上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你包扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫菲利特 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔·加勒特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我强行成为了这艘歌姬号的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号要为我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想抛弃平民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只顾自己逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真那样的话 你们早已经死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得确实没错 古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗大家的做法始终是不对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉上的你 至少让人感觉不会欺骗别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你 就好像换了个人似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现在的你手下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让菲利特 继续驾驶高达战斗的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在和UE的战斗中丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对UE出没规律的分析结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE潜伏在一座被弃置的要塞里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进行奇袭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果错过良机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE一定会继续扩大势力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 本舰歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在法丁尽可能补充战力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作气对UE实施打击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太蛮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和UE的战斗 交给联邦军去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的联邦军烂到了根上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算能驾驶高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是自私 太自私了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这是自私自利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚了的话 家人会担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 没有爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说我是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流在宇宙的客船上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一幸存的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔 德西尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好迟钝好迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像似曾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船上也有机动战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心别再受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是位可爱的小客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 举手投足跟你有那么点像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？像我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和德西尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两台UE的机动战士型入侵卫星内部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地联邦军启动防御系统开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统发现两台疑似UE机体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎已经到了卫星外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开高达去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特？是菲利特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击的高达没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能光看着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野 杰诺亚斯出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到高达被抢走激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫 杰诺亚斯特装型出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔 又在玩捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种姿态下打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管不知道是哪来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛮有两下子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像知道下次攻击从哪里来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 当时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉能预判敌人的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和接触德西尔时的感觉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩腻了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望还能见面 菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果到时候 哥哥还活着 的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔
